{
  "date_key": "2026-03-14",
  "date_cn": "2026年03月14日",
  "day_cn": "周六",
  "english": "<div style=\"background:#e8f0fe;border-left:4px solid #1a73e8;padding:10px 16px;margin:18px 0 10px;border-radius:0 6px 6px 0\"><strong style=\"color:#1a73e8;font-size:15px\">【今日主题】</strong><span style=\"margin-left:8px;font-weight:400;color:#1a73e8\">挑战与逆境（Adversity, Resilience, Change）</span></div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"background:#e3f2fd;border-left:4px solid #0d47a1;padding:10px 16px;margin:18px 0 10px;border-radius:0 6px 6px 0\"><strong style=\"color:#0d47a1;font-size:15px\">【英文原文】</strong></div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap\">A:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">Hey, you look beat. Everything okay?</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#e53935;white-space:nowrap\">B:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">Honestly? Not really. I got laid off last Friday. Totally <span style=\"background:#f5f0e6;color:#8b7355;padding:1px 4px;border-radius:3px;font-size:0.98em\">out of the blue</span>. I&#x27;ve been <strong>going through it</strong> all week — barely sleeping, overthinking everything.</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap\">A:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">Oh man, I&#x27;m sorry. That&#x27;s brutal. But knowing you, you&#x27;re not the type to just <strong>throw in the towel</strong>. You always find a way.</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#e53935;white-space:nowrap\">B:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">I appreciate that, but right now it feels like I&#x27;m just <strong>treading water</strong>, you know? Like I&#x27;m doing the bare minimum to not completely fall apart. Bills don&#x27;t stop just because your paycheck does.</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap\">A:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">Yeah, I hear you. But look — you&#x27;ve <strong>been through the wringer</strong> before. Remember when you moved here with basically nothing? You figured it out then, and you&#x27;ll figure it out now.</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#e53935;white-space:nowrap\">B:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">That&#x27;s true. I guess I just need to <strong>roll with the punches</strong> instead of fighting every little thing. My therapist keeps telling me to focus on what I can control.</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap\">A:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">Smart. And honestly, sometimes getting knocked down is what forces you to <strong>pivot</strong>. Maybe this is the push you needed to finally go after that UX design thing you&#x27;ve been talking about.</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#e53935;white-space:nowrap\">B:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">You know what, you might be right. I&#x27;ve been <strong>on the fence</strong> about it for months. Maybe it&#x27;s time to just <strong>take the leap</strong> and commit. Worst case, I learn something new.</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap\">A:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">Exactly. And hey, you don&#x27;t have to <strong>go it alone</strong>. I know a couple of people in that space — I can make some intros. Sometimes a little networking goes a long way.</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#e53935;white-space:nowrap\">B:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">That would mean a lot, seriously. I think I just needed someone to <strong>talk me off the ledge</strong> — not literally, obviously — just get me out of my own head.</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap\">A:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">That&#x27;s what friends are for. And for the record, I think a year from now you&#x27;ll <strong>look back on this</strong> and realize it was a <strong>blessing in disguise</strong>.</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#e53935;white-space:nowrap\">B:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">I hope so. Alright, enough moping. Let me buy you a coffee — it&#x27;s the least I can do.</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap\">A:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">Deal. But next year when you&#x27;re a <span style=\"background:#f5f0e6;color:#8b7355;padding:1px 4px;border-radius:3px;font-size:0.98em\">big-shot</span> UX designer, you&#x27;re buying me dinner.</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#e53935;white-space:nowrap\">B:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">Ha! You got it.</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"background:#e8f5e9;border-left:4px solid #1b5e20;padding:10px 16px;margin:18px 0 10px;border-radius:0 6px 6px 0\"><strong style=\"color:#1b5e20;font-size:15px\">【中文翻译】</strong></div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap\">A:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">嘿，你看起来很疲惫。还好吗？</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#e53935;white-space:nowrap\">B:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">说实话？不太好。上周五我被裁员了。完全<span style=\"background:#f5f0e6;color:#8b7355;padding:1px 4px;border-radius:3px;font-size:0.98em\">出乎意料</span>。这一整个星期我都<strong>很煎熬</strong>（going through it）——几乎睡不着，什么都想太多。</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap\">A:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">天哪，我很抱歉。那太残酷了。但我了解你，你不是那种会轻易<strong>认输放弃</strong>（throw in the towel）的人。你总能找到出路。</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#e53935;white-space:nowrap\">B:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">谢谢你这么说，但现在感觉我只是在<strong>勉强维持</strong>（treading water），你懂吗？就是做最低限度的事情来不让自己彻底崩溃。账单不会因为你没了工资就停下来。</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap\">A:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">是啊，我理解。但你看——你以前也<strong>经历过很多磨难</strong>（been through the wringer）。还记得你当初几乎什么都没有就搬到这儿来吗？那时候你搞定了，现在也会搞定的。</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#e53935;white-space:nowrap\">B:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">说得对。我想我需要学会<strong>随机应变、逆来顺受</strong>（roll with the punches），而不是跟每件小事较劲。我的心理咨询师一直让我专注于我能控制的事情。</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap\">A:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">很明智。而且说实话，有时候被击倒反而会迫使你<strong>转型</strong>（pivot）。也许这正是你需要的推动力，终于可以去追求你一直在说的UX设计了。</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#e53935;white-space:nowrap\">B:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">你说得可能对。我已经<span style=\"background:#f5f0e6;color:#8b7355;padding:1px 4px;border-radius:3px;font-size:0.98em\">犹豫不决</span>好几个月了。也许是时候<strong>放手一搏</strong>（take the leap）、全力投入了。最坏的情况，也不过是学到了新东西。</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap\">A:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">就是这样。而且，你不必<strong>孤军奋战</strong>（go it alone）。我认识几个做这行的人——我可以帮你介绍一下。有时候多认识几个人真的很有用。</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#e53935;white-space:nowrap\">B:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">那真的太感谢了，说真的。我觉得我就是需要有人<strong>把我从崩溃边缘拉回来</strong>（talk me off the ledge）——当然不是字面意思——就是让我别钻牛角尖。</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap\">A:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">朋友就是干这个的。而且我跟你说，我觉得一年以后你<strong>回头看这件事</strong>（look back on this），会意识到这其实是<strong>因祸得福</strong>（blessing in disguise）。</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#e53935;white-space:nowrap\">B:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">但愿如此。好了，不丧了。我请你喝杯咖啡——这是我最起码能做的。</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap\">A:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">成交。但明年你成了<span style=\"background:#f5f0e6;color:#8b7355;padding:1px 4px;border-radius:3px;font-size:0.98em\">大人物</span>UX设计师的时候，你得请我吃饭。</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#e53935;white-space:nowrap\">B:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">哈！没问题。</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"background:#f3e5f5;border-left:4px solid #4a148c;padding:10px 16px;margin:18px 0 10px;border-radius:0 6px 6px 0\"><strong style=\"color:#4a148c;font-size:15px\">【本日表达列表】</strong></div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:6px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 8px 10px 14px;color:#1a73e8;font-weight:700;font-size:13px;white-space:nowrap;background:#f0f4ff;border-radius:8px 0 0 8px;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-right:none\">01.</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 14px 10px 8px;background:#f8f9ff;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-left:none\"><strong style=\"color:#1a73e8;font-size:14px\"><strong>going through it</strong></strong><span style=\"color:#555;font-size:13px;margin-left:8px\">— 正在经历非常艰难的时期，精神或情感上很煎熬</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f0fe;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">📍 美国通用 / 当代流行（Gen Z-Millennial 高频使用）</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f5e9;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#2e7d32;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">💬 朋友之间倾诉困境、谈论低谷期</span></td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:6px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 8px 10px 14px;color:#1a73e8;font-weight:700;font-size:13px;white-space:nowrap;background:#f0f4ff;border-radius:8px 0 0 8px;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-right:none\">02.</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 14px 10px 8px;background:#f8f9ff;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-left:none\"><strong style=\"color:#1a73e8;font-size:14px\"><strong>throw in the towel</strong></strong><span style=\"color:#555;font-size:13px;margin-left:8px\">— 认输，放弃（源自拳击比赛中扔毛巾认输的动作）</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f0fe;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">📍 美国通用 / 全球通用</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f5e9;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#2e7d32;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">💬 鼓励别人不要放弃，或承认自己放弃了某事</span></td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:6px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 8px 10px 14px;color:#1a73e8;font-weight:700;font-size:13px;white-space:nowrap;background:#f0f4ff;border-radius:8px 0 0 8px;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-right:none\">03.</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 14px 10px 8px;background:#f8f9ff;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-left:none\"><strong style=\"color:#1a73e8;font-size:14px\"><strong>treading water</strong></strong><span style=\"color:#555;font-size:13px;margin-left:8px\">— 原地踏步，勉强维持现状，没有进步也没有倒退</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f0fe;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">📍 美国通用</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f5e9;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#2e7d32;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">💬 描述工作、财务或生活状态停滞不前</span></td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:6px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 8px 10px 14px;color:#1a73e8;font-weight:700;font-size:13px;white-space:nowrap;background:#f0f4ff;border-radius:8px 0 0 8px;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-right:none\">04.</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 14px 10px 8px;background:#f8f9ff;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-left:none\"><strong style=\"color:#1a73e8;font-size:14px\"><strong>been through the wringer</strong></strong><span style=\"color:#555;font-size:13px;margin-left:8px\">— 经历了极其艰苦的磨难或折磨（wringer 指老式衣物脱水机的压辊）</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f0fe;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">📍 美国通用</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f5e9;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#2e7d32;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">💬 形容某人饱经磨难后的状态</span></td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:6px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 8px 10px 14px;color:#1a73e8;font-weight:700;font-size:13px;white-space:nowrap;background:#f0f4ff;border-radius:8px 0 0 8px;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-right:none\">05.</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 14px 10px 8px;background:#f8f9ff;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-left:none\"><strong style=\"color:#1a73e8;font-size:14px\"><strong>roll with the punches</strong></strong><span style=\"color:#555;font-size:13px;margin-left:8px\">— 随机应变，坦然接受困难和打击（源自拳击中顺着对方出拳方向转身以减轻冲击）</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f0fe;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">📍 美国通用 / 全球通用</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f5e9;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#2e7d32;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">💬 建议别人面对逆境要灵活应对</span></td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:6px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 8px 10px 14px;color:#1a73e8;font-weight:700;font-size:13px;white-space:nowrap;background:#f0f4ff;border-radius:8px 0 0 8px;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-right:none\">06.</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 14px 10px 8px;background:#f8f9ff;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-left:none\"><strong style=\"color:#1a73e8;font-size:14px\"><strong>pivot</strong></strong><span style=\"color:#555;font-size:13px;margin-left:8px\">— （在事业或人生方向上）转型、转变方向</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f0fe;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">📍 美国通用（尤其硅谷/职场/创业圈高频使用）</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f5e9;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#2e7d32;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">💬 讨论职业变动、公司战略调整、人生转折</span></td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:6px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 8px 10px 14px;color:#1a73e8;font-weight:700;font-size:13px;white-space:nowrap;background:#f0f4ff;border-radius:8px 0 0 8px;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-right:none\">07.</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 14px 10px 8px;background:#f8f9ff;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-left:none\"><strong style=\"color:#1a73e8;font-size:14px\"><strong>take the leap</strong></strong><span style=\"color:#555;font-size:13px;margin-left:8px\">— 放手一搏，鼓起勇气迈出重要的一步（尤其指有风险的决定）</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f0fe;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">📍 美国通用</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f5e9;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#2e7d32;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">💬 鼓励别人做出重大决定，如换工作、创业、搬家</span></td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:6px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 8px 10px 14px;color:#1a73e8;font-weight:700;font-size:13px;white-space:nowrap;background:#f0f4ff;border-radius:8px 0 0 8px;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-right:none\">08.</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 14px 10px 8px;background:#f8f9ff;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-left:none\"><strong style=\"color:#1a73e8;font-size:14px\"><strong>go it alone</strong></strong><span style=\"color:#555;font-size:13px;margin-left:8px\">— 独自行动，孤军奋战，不依赖他人的帮助</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f0fe;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">📍 美国通用 / 全球通用</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f5e9;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#2e7d32;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">💬 讨论创业、面对挑战时是否寻求帮助</span></td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:6px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 8px 10px 14px;color:#1a73e8;font-weight:700;font-size:13px;white-space:nowrap;background:#f0f4ff;border-radius:8px 0 0 8px;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-right:none\">09.</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 14px 10px 8px;background:#f8f9ff;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-left:none\"><strong style=\"color:#1a73e8;font-size:14px\"><strong>talk someone off the ledge</strong></strong><span style=\"color:#555;font-size:13px;margin-left:8px\">— 在某人极度焦虑或崩溃时安抚他们、把他们从情绪崩溃边缘拉回来（非字面意义，日常口语中比喻用法非常普遍）</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f0fe;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">📍 美国通用</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f5e9;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#2e7d32;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">💬 朋友之间互相安慰、工作压力大时同事间支持</span></td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:6px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 8px 10px 14px;color:#1a73e8;font-weight:700;font-size:13px;white-space:nowrap;background:#f0f4ff;border-radius:8px 0 0 8px;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-right:none\">10.</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 14px 10px 8px;background:#f8f9ff;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-left:none\"><strong style=\"color:#1a73e8;font-size:14px\"><strong>blessing in disguise</strong></strong><span style=\"color:#555;font-size:13px;margin-left:8px\">— 因祸得福，表面看是坏事但实际上带来了好结果</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f0fe;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">📍 美国通用 / 全球通用</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f5e9;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#2e7d32;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">💬 事后回顾不幸经历时的感悟，安慰正在经历困难的人</span></td></tr></table>",
  "beauty": "<div style=\"background:#fce4ec;border-left:4px solid #e91e8c;padding:10px 16px;margin:18px 0 10px;border-radius:0 6px 6px 0\"><strong style=\"color:#c2185b;font-size:15px\">【今日主题】</strong><span style=\"margin-left:8px;font-weight:400;color:#c2185b\">🪞 完整妆容教程——橄榄皮圆脸の「初春轻暖棕」全流程</span></div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">&gt; 🌸 三月中旬，气温回暖、光线柔和，今天这套妆容以 <strong>暖棕色系</strong> 为主调，整体思路是：<strong>底妆矫色提亮→修容视觉瘦脸→眼妆拉长→唇妆点题</strong>。全程约 25 分钟，每一步都为你的肤质和脸型量身拆解。</p>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"color:#c2185b;font-weight:700;font-size:15px;margin:16px 0 6px;padding-bottom:4px;border-bottom:1px solid #fce4ec\">▎STEP 0 · 妆前准备（3 min）</div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"display:flex;align-items:flex-start;margin:8px 0;padding:10px 14px;background:#fdf0f7;border-radius:8px\"><span style=\"color:#e91e8c;font-weight:700;min-width:70px;font-size:13px\">1.</span><span style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7\"><strong>洁面后护肤</strong>：轻薄水乳即可，避免过度滋润导致后续搓泥。</span></div>\n<div style=\"display:flex;align-items:flex-start;margin:8px 0;padding:10px 14px;background:#fdf0f7;border-radius:8px\"><span style=\"color:#e91e8c;font-weight:700;min-width:70px;font-size:13px\">2.</span><span style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7\"><strong>等待 5 分钟</strong>：让护肤品充分吸收，用这个时间整理工具。</span></div>\n<div style=\"display:flex;align-items:flex-start;margin:8px 0;padding:10px 14px;background:#fdf0f7;border-radius:8px\"><span style=\"color:#e91e8c;font-weight:700;min-width:70px;font-size:13px\">3.</span><span style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7\"><strong>妆前需要准备的工具</strong>：</span></div>\n<div style=\"padding:4px 0 4px 16px;color:#444;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7\"><span style=\"color:#e91e8c;margin-right:8px\">✦</span>美妆蛋 × 1（微湿）</div>\n<div style=\"padding:4px 0 4px 16px;color:#444;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7\"><span style=\"color:#e91e8c;margin-right:8px\">✦</span>修容刷（斜角中号）× 1</div>\n<div style=\"padding:4px 0 4px 16px;color:#444;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7\"><span style=\"color:#e91e8c;margin-right:8px\">✦</span>眼影刷（铺色 + 晕染 + 细节）× 3</div>\n<div style=\"padding:4px 0 4px 16px;color:#444;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7\"><span style=\"color:#e91e8c;margin-right:8px\">✦</span>唇刷 × 1（可选）</div>\n<div style=\"padding:4px 0 4px 16px;color:#444;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7\"><span style=\"color:#e91e8c;margin-right:8px\">✦</span>散粉扑/蜜粉刷 × 1</div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"color:#c2185b;font-weight:700;font-size:15px;margin:16px 0 6px;padding-bottom:4px;border-bottom:1px solid #fce4ec\">▎STEP 1 · 妆前乳（1 min）</div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">| 区域 | 用什么 | 为什么 |</p>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">|------|--------|--------|</p>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">| 全脸 | <strong>控油妆前乳</strong>（哑光/柔焦质地） | 你角质层偏厚、毛孔偏大，需要填平毛孔、控制油光 |</p>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">| T区额外 | 毛孔隐形膏，逆毛孔方向按压 | 圆脸额头与鼻翼毛孔易显粗 |</p>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">| 两颊/下巴 | 叠加一层 <strong>绿色矫色隔离</strong>（薄薄一层） | 中和橄榄皮偏黄偏暗的色调 |</p>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">&gt; ⚠️ 切记：绿色隔离只用在暗沉/泛黄区域，不要全脸涂，否则后续粉底会发灰。</p>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"color:#c2185b;font-weight:700;font-size:15px;margin:16px 0 6px;padding-bottom:4px;border-bottom:1px solid #fce4ec\">▎STEP 2 · 底妆（3 min）</div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\"><strong>方法：「中心向外」点涂法 + 美妆蛋弹压</strong></p>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"display:flex;align-items:flex-start;margin:8px 0;padding:10px 14px;background:#fdf0f7;border-radius:8px\"><span style=\"color:#e91e8c;font-weight:700;min-width:70px;font-size:13px\">1.</span><span style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7\">取粉底液（约一泵半），点在额头、鼻梁、双颊内侧、下巴 <strong>五点</strong>。</span></div>\n<div style=\"display:flex;align-items:flex-start;margin:8px 0;padding:10px 14px;background:#fdf0f7;border-radius:8px\"><span style=\"color:#e91e8c;font-weight:700;min-width:70px;font-size:13px\">2.</span><span style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7\">用 <strong>微湿美妆蛋</strong> 从面部中心向外弹压推开——</span></div>\n<div style=\"padding:4px 0 4px 16px;color:#444;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7\"><span style=\"color:#e91e8c;margin-right:8px\">✦</span>面中区域（鼻翼、眼下、苹果肌）：多弹几次，遮盖力集中在这里。</div>\n<div style=\"padding:4px 0 4px 16px;color:#444;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7\"><span style=\"color:#e91e8c;margin-right:8px\">✦</span>脸部边缘（发际线、下颌线）：轻轻带过即可，<strong>不要边缘厚重</strong>，圆脸最忌底妆&quot;面具感&quot;把脸框得更圆。</div>\n<div style=\"display:flex;align-items:flex-start;margin:8px 0;padding:10px 14px;background:#fdf0f7;border-radius:8px\"><span style=\"color:#e91e8c;font-weight:700;min-width:70px;font-size:13px\">3.</span><span style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7\">痘印/色素沉着：用遮瑕膏 <strong>点涂→按压→边缘拍开</strong>，不要拖拽。</span></div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">&gt; 🎯 <strong>色号选择关键</strong>：橄榄皮一定选 <strong>黄调偏暖（warm/golden undertone）</strong> 的色号，避免粉调/冷调底妆，否则脸会显灰显脏。</p>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"color:#c2185b;font-weight:700;font-size:15px;margin:16px 0 6px;padding-bottom:4px;border-bottom:1px solid #fce4ec\">▎STEP 3 · 遮瑕（2 min）</div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">| 区域 | 手法 | 要点 |</p>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">|------|------|------|</p>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">| 黑眼圈 | 倒三角形遮瑕，蛋尖按压 | 选比底妆亮半号的 <strong>暖桃色调</strong> 遮瑕，同时提亮面中 |</p>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">| 鼻翼暗沉 | 薄薄一层遮瑕，指腹拍匀 | 橄榄皮鼻翼特别容易暗，这步很关键 |</p>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">| 法令纹/嘴角 | 细刷点涂 | 圆脸法令纹区域提亮可以拉长中庭视觉 |</p>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"color:#c2185b;font-weight:700;font-size:15px;margin:16px 0 6px;padding-bottom:4px;border-bottom:1px solid #fce4ec\">▎STEP 4 · 定妆（1 min）</div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"padding:4px 0 4px 16px;color:#444;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7\"><span style=\"color:#e91e8c;margin-right:8px\">✦</span><strong>T区 + 鼻翼</strong>：用 <strong>控油散粉</strong> 按压定妆（你出油适中，薄按即可）。</div>\n<div style=\"padding:4px 0 4px 16px;color:#444;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7\"><span style=\"color:#e91e8c;margin-right:8px\">✦</span><strong>眼下/面中</strong>：用烘焙法 or 极少量散粉轻扫，<strong>保留微光泽感</strong>——橄榄皮全哑光会显老显干。</div>\n<div style=\"padding:4px 0 4px 16px;color:#444;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7\"><span style=\"color:#e91e8c;margin-right:8px\">✦</span><strong>面部边缘</strong>：不定妆或极轻扫过，保持皮肤质感自然过渡。</div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"color:#c2185b;font-weight:700;font-size:15px;margin:16px 0 6px;padding-bottom:4px;border-bottom:1px solid #fce4ec\">▎STEP 5 · 修容 + 高光（3 min）⭐ 圆脸核心步骤</div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">这一步对你的脸型改变最大，请认真看：</p>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"color:#c2185b;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;margin:16px 0 6px;padding-bottom:4px;border-bottom:1px solid #fce4ec\">🔲 修容（收窄 + 拉长）</div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">```</p>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">修容位置示意（正面看）：</p>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">╭──  发际线两侧（太阳穴向上）──╮</p>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">╱                                  ╲</p>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">│  颧骨下方 ← 从耳前向嘴角方向斜扫   │</p>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">│                                    │</p>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">╲   下颌角 → 向下巴方向收           ╱</p>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">╰──────── 下巴底部（可选）────────╯</p>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">```</p>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"padding:4px 0 4px 16px;color:#444;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7\"><span style=\"color:#e91e8c;margin-right:8px\">✦</span><strong>发际线两侧</strong>：收窄额头横向宽度——圆脸重点！</div>\n<div style=\"padding:4px 0 4px 16px;color:#444;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7\"><span style=\"color:#e91e8c;margin-right:8px\">✦</span><strong>颧骨下方</strong>：从耳前向嘴角方向 <strong>斜向下</strong> 扫（不要横着扫，横扫显更宽）。</div>\n<div style=\"padding:4px 0 4px 16px;color:#444;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7\"><span style=\"color:#e91e8c;margin-right:8px\">✦</span><strong>下颌角到下巴</strong>：轻扫，制造下颌线条感。</div>\n<div style=\"padding:4px 0 4px 16px;color:#444;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7\"><span style=\"color:#e91e8c;margin-right:8px\">✦</span><strong>鼻侧影</strong>：从眉头向</div>",
  "research": "<div style=\"background:#fff;border:1px solid #e0e0e0;border-radius:10px;padding:20px 22px;margin:16px 0;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.06)\"><div style=\"background:linear-gradient(135deg,#00bcd4,#00897b);color:#fff;padding:10px 16px;border-radius:6px;margin:-20px -22px 16px;font-weight:700;font-size:15px;letter-spacing:1px\">📄 论文 1</div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#c62828;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">📌 作者：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;\">Dharel P. Acut</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#1565c0;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">📖 标题：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;font-weight:700;\">From classroom learning to real-world skills: an autoethnographic account of school field trips and STEM work immersion program management</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#00838f;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">📰 期刊：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;\">Disciplinary and Interdisciplinary Science Education Research</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#e65100;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">📅 年份：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;\">2024</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#2e7d32;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">📊 引用量：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;\">10 次</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#4a148c;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">📝 摘要：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;\">Abstract Quality science education is crucial in preparing students for real-world challenges by fostering scientific literacy and critical thinking skills. Field trips and work immersion programs support this goal by providing hands-on experiences and real-world applications of scientific concepts, thereby enhancing student engagement and understanding. This autoethnographic study explores the ma…</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#6a1b9a;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">🔗 与本研究的关联性：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;\">这篇论文与用户研究方向的关联性主要体现在方法论和教师经验维度。首先，该研究采用自我民族志（autoethnography）作为核心方法，与方向三中教师脆弱性与情感劳动研究所使用的自我民族志方法一致，可提供方法论上的参照与对话。其次，研究聚焦教师对课外教学活动（实地考察与实习项目）的管理与反思性实践，涉及教师在制度框架下的角色与情感体验，与方向三关注的教师与制度议题存在一定交集。不过，该研究的学科情境（</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#37474f;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">🆔 DOI：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"font-size:13px;line-height:1.7\"><a href=\"https://doi.org/10.1186/s43031-024-00111-x\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color:#1a73e8;text-decoration:none\">🔍 10.1186/s43031-024-00111-x</a></td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:6px\"></div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"background:#fff;border:1px solid #e0e0e0;border-radius:10px;padding:20px 22px;margin:16px 0;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.06)\"><div style=\"background:linear-gradient(135deg,#00bcd4,#00897b);color:#fff;padding:10px 16px;border-radius:6px;margin:-20px -22px 16px;font-weight:700;font-size:15px;letter-spacing:1px\">📄 论文 2</div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#c62828;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">📌 作者：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;\">Katarina Blennow, Martin Malmström, Elizabeth Petroelje Stolle</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#1565c0;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">📖 标题：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;font-weight:700;\">Countering Discourses of Derision: Moving towards Action in Teacher Education in the USA and Sweden</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#00838f;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">📰 期刊：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;\">Education Sciences</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#e65100;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">📅 年份：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;\">2023</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#2e7d32;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">📊 引用量：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;\">3 次</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#4a148c;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">📝 摘要：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;\">This article is about how negative discourses of teacher education position teacher educators and how they might influence or inspire action. We use self-study methods to investigate the political dimension of teacher education in two national contexts: Sweden and the USA. More specifically, we examine the emotions stirred by the positioning related to being a teacher educator and how those emotio…</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#6a1b9a;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">🔗 与本研究的关联性：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;\">本文聚焦教师教育者如何被负面话语定位及其情感回应，与<strong>方向三（教师与制度）</strong>高度相关：研究涉及教师在制度性话语中的脆弱性（teacher vulnerability）、面对贬抑话语时的情感劳动（emotional labor），以及运用自我研究方法（与autoethnography同属质性自我探究传统）来抵抗职业边界的限制。此外，文章对负面话语的批判分析也与<strong>方向一</strong>中批判话语分析（CDA）及认识不公正（epistemic injustice）的关切存在方法论与理论上的交叉，即制度话语如何</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#37474f;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">🆔 DOI：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"font-size:13px;line-height:1.7\"><a href=\"https://doi.org/10.3390/educsci13070635\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color:#1a73e8;text-decoration:none\">🔍 10.3390/educsci13070635</a></td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:6px\"></div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"background:#fff;border:1px solid #e0e0e0;border-radius:10px;padding:20px 22px;margin:16px 0;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.06)\"><div style=\"background:linear-gradient(135deg,#00bcd4,#00897b);color:#fff;padding:10px 16px;border-radius:6px;margin:-20px -22px 16px;font-weight:700;font-size:15px;letter-spacing:1px\">📄 论文 3</div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#c62828;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">📌 作者：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;\">Francesca Ferrer-Best</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#1565c0;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">📖 标题：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;font-weight:700;\">The Virtual Ballet Studio: A Phenomenological Enquiry into the Domestic as Dance-Space During Lockdown</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#00838f;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">📰 期刊：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;\">The International Journal of Screendance</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#e65100;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">📅 年份：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;\">2021</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#2e7d32;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">📊 引用量：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;\">5 次</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#4a148c;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">📝 摘要：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;\">The paper is based on an autoethnographic study of dancing via Zoom over the Covid19 lockdown in Sydney, Australia. Its theoretical framework takes up Iris Marion Young&#x27;s critical phenomenology and work on domestic space to think about certain focal points of the experience, such as having a room to move in, the floor, and the screen. The aim is to examine how important dance-space is to the exper…</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#6a1b9a;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">🔗 与本研究的关联性：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;\">这篇论文与用户研究方向的关联性较为有限，但存在方法论上的交叉。该研究采用<strong>自我民族志（autoethnography）</strong>方法探究疫情封锁期间居家空间转化为舞蹈空间的现象学体验，这与方向三中教师研究所使用的自我民族志方法论相呼应，可为理解该方法如何捕捉身体化、情感化的主体经验提供跨学科参照。此外，其对空间、屏幕（Zoom）中介下身体实践的关注，也可间接启发方向二中对线上课堂互动与中介工具如何重</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#37474f;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">🆔 DOI：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"font-size:13px;line-height:1.7\"><a href=\"https://doi.org/10.18061/ijsd.v12i0.7812\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color:#1a73e8;text-decoration:none\">🔍 10.18061/ijsd.v12i0.7812</a></td></tr></table>\n</div>"
